                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18171029-126-defend754 t18171029-126-deflabel674"></join>; on the 14th of October, I missed the seal bottoms.</p>
               <p>WILLIAM HARRIS. I am a servant to Mr. Cropley. I missed the seal bottoms, and asked the prisoner if he knew anything about them - He confessed taking them, and produced one.</p>
